node.text:
Staying fit and maintaining my muscle mass during these hard times👊🏻 All you need for this workout is a resistance tube and a mini band. 
Perform 3 rounds of each circuit before moving on to the next:

1a: one arm shoulder press - 15 reps ea
1b: biceps curl - 15 reps slow descent
1c: rows - 15 reps

2a: pull down - 15 reps
2b: chest press - 15 reps
2c: one legged RDL - 15 reps ea

3a: slow descent squats - 15 reps
3b: triceps overhead - 15 reps
3c: narrow push ups - 15 reps

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dolph Lundgren on July 06, 2021 tagging @officialslystallone. May be an image of 2 people and people standing.

node.text: A young actor taking direction from the bossman back in the good ol’ days. Happy Birthday, Sly!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dolph Lundgren on July 04, 2021. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Let’s enjoy ourselves today! Happy 4th America🇺🇸🍾

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dolph Lundgren on July 03, 2021 tagging @emmakrokdal. May be an image of 2 people.

node.text: A one two punch: Emma’s Bday and the 4th of July weekend! 🍾🇳🇴🇺🇸

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dolph Lundgren on June 26, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, beard and beach.

node.text: Midsummer in Malibu - Almost as good as in Sweden🍾🇸🇪

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dolph Lundgren on June 20, 2021 tagging @thescottadkins. May be an image of 2 people, Persian cat and indoor.

node.text: Getting some expert help to finish the mix for my latest film CASTLE FALLS.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dolph Lundgren on June 11, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and food.

node.text: Enjoying some Spaghetti Vongole. Life’s good. Enjoy your weekend!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dolph Lundgren on June 03, 2021 tagging @stockholmskyokushin. May be an image of 2 people, people standing, indoor and text.

node.text: Haven’t been back to my home country Sweden for a year because of the pandemic. Can’t wait to get back and see my brothers and sisters. I know a lot of families are in the same situation. Also, I’ll get a chance to practice karate with my teacher Brian Fitkin who I started  training with when I was 15. OSU! 👊

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dolph Lundgren on May 31, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, people standing, outdoors and tree.

node.text: Standing at the LA National Cemetery is a special experience. It gives you perspective. Have a great Memorial Day!

node.text: Got this cute letter in the mail. From a little girl who was born 30 years after Rocky IV was made. Makes it all feel worthwhile. Swipe and it gets better...🙏
